Geoff Corpe stays at MSAS as UK managing director . MSAS Cargo International UK managing director Geoff Corpe will remain with the international freight forwarding group contrary to an announcement in September that he would join British Airways Air Cargo . " MSAS UK and BA Cargo , both , are in the middle of exciting and challenging programmes that promise considerable change for the future . And , I believe it is very important that I see through to completion a number of projects at MSAS UK in which I have had personal involvement . " Corpe said in a statement . MSAS has 5 , 500 employees in 30 countries and agents in a further 84 countries is part of the Ocean Group plc . - - Air Cargo Newsroom Tel + 44 171 542 7706 Fax + 44 171 542 5017 
